@NODE MI_M_Project_Load "Project menu"

 @{b}Load@{ub}

  Load a some leagues you have saved. Leagues already loaded are removed.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MI_M_Project_Append "Project menu"

 @{b}Append@{ub}

  Append leagues to the list of leagues. If there already are leagues in
  they will therefore not be removed.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MI_M_Project_Save "Project menu"

 @{b}Save@{ub}

  Save all the leagues in the listview to a file.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MI_M_Project_About "Project menu"

 @{b}About@{ub}

  Miscellaneous information on Leagues.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MI_M_Project_Quit "Project menu"

 @{b}Quit@{ub}

  Quits Leagues. Remember to @{"save" LINK MI_M_Project_Save} the leagues before quitting.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MI_M_Preferences_Edit "Preferences menu"

 @{b}Miscellaneous@{ub}

  Pressing @{b}Okay@{ub} affects Leagues immediately. Pressing @{b}Cancel@{ub} will abort
  the changes you have made.

  @{b}Screen Mode@{ub}

   Select the screen mode you want Leagues to be in.

   The screen is public so you can put other windows on to Leagues. The
   name of the screen is 'Leagues'.

  @{b}Font@{ub}

   The font which will be used for everything besides listviews.

  @{b}List view font@{ub}

   This font is used in all listviews.

  @{b}Palette@{ub}

   Well, kind a speaks for it self doesn't it...

  @{b}Scroller width@{ub}

   The width of the scrollers in listviews.
@ENDNODE

@NODE MI_M_Preferences_SavePrefs "Preferences menu"

 @{b}Save@{ub}

  Save preferences.
@ENDNODE

